Detailed Description

cvmx_dfa_debug1

When the DFA_CONTROL[SBDLCK] bit is written '1', the contents of this register are locked down. Otherwise, the contents of this register are the 'active' contents of the DFA Scoreboard at the time of the CSR read operation. VERIFICATION NOTE: Read data is unsafe. X's(undefined data) can propagate (in the behavioral model) on the read operations unless the DTE Engine specified by DFA_CONTROL[SBDNUM] has previously been assigned an instruction.
